    "short_excerpt": "Middleware \u00b6",
    "source_id": "fastapi-middleware",
    "source_type": "official_doc",
    "span_id": "fastapi-middleware-1",
    "text": "Middleware \u00b6",
    "url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/"
  },
  {
    "captured_at": "2026-05-26T08:42:53.083772Z",
    "final_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/",
    "quote_hash": "sha256:8d190e012969d14243d1fc622a656af9bb3b7ea61fb1b15ee75bdc8f98bdce0e",
    "section_anchor": "root",
    "short_excerpt": "You can add middleware to FastAPI applications.",
    "source_id": "fastapi-middleware",
    "source_type": "official_doc",
    "span_id": "fastapi-middleware-2",
    "text": "You can add middleware to FastAPI applications.",
    "url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/"
  },
  {
    "captured_at": "2026-05-26T08:42:53.083772Z",
    "final_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/",
    "quote_hash": "sha256:3f26cc136e3edc6f6141a3d602e6b905df9d7c348dda4fee7c3cee28dfbddbdd",
    "section_anchor": "root",
    "short_excerpt": "A \"middleware\" is a function that works with every request before it is processed by any specific path operation . And also with every response before returning it.",
    "source_id": "fastapi-middleware",
    "source_type": "official_doc",
    "span_id": "fastapi-middleware-3",
    "text": "A \"middleware\" is a function that works with every request before it is processed by any specific path operation . And also with every response before returning it.",
    "url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/"
  },
  {
    "captured_at": "2026-05-26T08:42:53.083772Z",
    "final_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/",
    "quote_hash": "sha256:fac3dd7073b8bc4797343e1153e130ebbf82e6912e9ce8eaaf7c61e3606041aa",
    "section_anchor": "root",
    "short_excerpt": "It takes each request that comes to your application.",
    "source_id": "fastapi-middleware",
    "source_type": "official_doc",
    "span_id": "fastapi-middleware-4",
    "text": "It takes each request that comes to your application.",
    "url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/"
  },
  {
    "captured_at": "2026-05-26T08:42:53.083772Z",
    "final_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/",
    "quote_hash": "sha256:49aaa322e60b3817f0a29a3c194ac0d851e85a0ac3b2e9e232bec31f20737fa4",
    "section_anchor": "root",
    "short_excerpt": "It can then do something to that request or run any needed code.",
    "source_id": "fastapi-middleware",
    "source_type": "official_doc",
    "span_id": "fastapi-middleware-5",
    "text": "It can then do something to that request or run any needed code.",
    "url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/"
  },
  {
    "captured_at": "2026-05-26T08:42:53.083772Z",
    "final_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/",
    "quote_hash": "sha256:43b0f34c901d40a25c9e61869f6fa57603aef5bedc8a9e8112f4d9f65eeefd3e",
    "section_anchor": "root",
    "short_excerpt": "Then it passes the request to be processed by the rest of the application (by some path operation ).",
    "source_id": "fastapi-middleware",
    "source_type": "official_doc",
    "span_id": "fastapi-middleware-6",
    "text": "Then it passes the request to be processed by the rest of the application (by some path operation ).",
    "url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/"
  },
  {
    "captured_at": "2026-05-26T08:42:53.083772Z",
    "final_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/",
    "quote_hash": "sha256:5b43292cbb07c37db42b7599149323eae3990295a3c655f487aec731d6237696",
    "section_anchor": "root",
    "short_excerpt": "It then takes the response generated by the application (by some path operation ).",
    "source_id": "fastapi-middleware",
    "source_type": "official_doc",
    "span_id": "fastapi-middleware-7",
    "text": "It then takes the response generated by the application (by some path operation ).",
    "url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/"
  },
  {
    "captured_at": "2026-05-26T08:42:53.083772Z",
    "final_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/",
    "quote_hash": "sha256:2923f5e768071c7a2a640510c17868d8fdbeaa3194d83030f859aa2faa2f7111",
    "section_anchor": "root",
    "short_excerpt": "It can do something to that response or run any needed code.",
    "source_id": "fastapi-middleware",
    "source_type": "official_doc",
    "span_id": "fastapi-middleware-8",
    "text": "It can do something to that response or run any needed code.",
    "url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/"
  },
  {
    "captured_at": "2026-05-26T08:42:53.083772Z",
    "final_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/",
    "quote_hash": "sha256:1a11044f8cc3f78dea25dae2db1a2e2e1dd68d6d7565e9d51eb88eb3d5b94465",
    "section_anchor": "root",
    "short_excerpt": "Then it returns the response .",
    "source_id": "fastapi-middleware",
    "source_type": "official_doc",
    "span_id": "fastapi-middleware-9",
    "text": "Then it returns the response .",
    "url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/"
  },
  {
    "captured_at": "2026-05-26T08:42:53.083772Z",
