    "section_anchor": "root",
    "short_excerpt": "Technical Details",
    "source_id": "fastapi-middleware",
    "source_type": "official_doc",
    "span_id": "fastapi-middleware-10",
    "text": "Technical Details",
    "url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/"
  },
  {
    "captured_at": "2026-05-26T08:42:53.083772Z",
    "final_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/",
    "quote_hash": "sha256:4df7fb866d6da2dd679b22b9c54855373dd102ae8d596826858adad8561910da",
    "section_anchor": "root",
    "short_excerpt": "If you have dependencies with yield , the exit code will run after the middleware.",
    "source_id": "fastapi-middleware",
    "source_type": "official_doc",
    "span_id": "fastapi-middleware-11",
    "text": "If you have dependencies with yield , the exit code will run after the middleware.",
    "url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/"
  },
  {
    "captured_at": "2026-05-26T08:42:53.083772Z",
    "final_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/",
    "quote_hash": "sha256:350e32e0f6dd2aad034b7d4d1416faccd6181ef17c918ceb20ee94bf42f8290b",
    "section_anchor": "root",
    "short_excerpt": "If there were any background tasks (covered in the Background Tasks section, you will see it later), they will run after all the middleware.",
    "source_id": "fastapi-middleware",
    "source_type": "official_doc",
    "span_id": "fastapi-middleware-12",
    "text": "If there were any background tasks (covered in the Background Tasks section, you will see it later), they will run after all the middleware.",
    "url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/"
  },
