    "section_anchor": "root",
    "short_excerpt": "When you add multiple middlewares using either @app.middleware() decorator or app.add_middleware() method, each new middleware wraps the application, forming a stack. The last middleware added is the outermost , and the first is the innermost .",
    "source_id": "fastapi-middleware",
    "source_type": "official_doc",
    "span_id": "fastapi-middleware-35",
    "text": "When you add multiple middlewares using either @app.middleware() decorator or app.add_middleware() method, each new middleware wraps the application, forming a stack. The last middleware added is the outermost , and the first is the innermost .",
    "url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/middleware/"
  },
